<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Your Booking</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BR/>
Dear <B>$!name,</B>
<BR/>
<BR/>
Thank you for booking your cab at $!organization. Please find the details of your booking(s) below.
<BR/>
<BR/>
<table border="1" cellpadding="3">
    <tbody>
    <tr>
        <th>From</th>
        <th>To</th> 
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Time</th>

    </tr>
        #foreach( $!booking in $!bookingList )
        <tr>
            <td>$!booking.pickupStreetAddress</td>
            <td>$!booking.dropStreetAddress</td>  
            <td>$!booking.bookingType</td>          
            <td>$!booking.pickupTime</td>
        </tr>
        #end
    </tbody>
</table>
<BR/>
This is an automated email message generated by $!organization. Please do not reply.
<BR/>
<BR/>
Best Regards,
<BR/>
$!organization
</BODY>
</HTML>